data.description: Here is your opportunity to own this beautiful lake home. This home has panoramic views of the lake and is perfect for a primary or vacation home, with a potential for a rental property, No HOA'S. Close proximity to Lake picnic area/miles of hiking trails. The family room opens to the kitchen and breakfast area, it has wood vaulted ceilings with stone fireplace. Kitchen has the following: Stainless-steel appliances, cherry wood cabinets bar seating, granite counters. The front living/dining area features crown moldings with picture windows. The main bedroom is spacious and isolated on the first floor. Main bedroom restroom includes granite counters cherry wood cabinets, walk in shower & a separate jetted tub with amazing views. Additional features include a wraparound porch with mature landscaping, real wood blinds, cherry wood cabinets, hardwood floors throughout, fans throughout, tile floors in all bathrooms and laundry area. All bedrooms have walk in closets. The upstairs includes a large spacious walk-in room/closet to suit your storage needs. You can enjoy a scenic sunset in the spacious back covered patio where there is the built-in bench for extra seating, the stone-built fountain is a plus. There is a direct propane connection for your grill and is ready for you to entertain guests. There is ample parking on the cul-de-sac street. You must see it in person, please call to schedule a showing!
